{"tid":1697673,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"無論真假，何鳩堯呢單野唔可以再傾，要focus番係周梓樂單野到","createTime":"2019-11-07T03:56:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-08T02:48:11.000Z","uid":188176,"like":28,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"251f0829dcbdbe0e0d8b089d9e4dd3a87e433274","tid":1697673,"uid":188176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T03:56:44.000Z","msg":"可能好難聽，不過其實大家心中都明白<br />\n周梓樂係無可能康復行番出醫院<br />\n而佢既情況三日內一定會塵埃落定<br />\n梓樂單野，警犬一定係責無旁貸<br />\n唔係佢地痴左線日日出催淚彈四圍打人，情況根本唔會惡化到而家咁<br />\n唔係佢地攻入停車場，根本唔會出事<br />\n唔係佢地截停部救護車，早三十分鐘送院<br />\n早d開腦救人放血，救得番既機會一定相當大<br />\n問題係如果三日後大家都心中有數既情況出現左<br />\n咁究竟應該做d乜先係面家最重要既事<br />\n唔可以再煮到埋黎先食"},{"pid":"d37561b77576362ba52847240e50a936a8eee04b","tid":1697673,"uid":188176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T03:59:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5a925db57144c7860554e4aa097735233cea77f","tid":1697673,"uid":77788,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T04:01:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"36097f6d7d44dece7fc25cbf2c8316883927a218","tid":1697673,"uid":301361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T04:02:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望科大呢位手足可以過到呢關，黑警要死全家！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e12be46c78be1083a01bb02e28db2b94ee6bb6dd","tid":1697673,"uid":36716,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T04:03:31.000Z","msg":"原來100%肯定就係佢<br />\n你上面講既野我認同既<br />\n我幫你推<br />\n但我都要屌鳩你屈個義士!!!"},{"pid":"763957d751e6eb447ffe36da1262f426006793dc","tid":1697673,"uid":250511,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a5a925